{"tid":2486304,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找消失十年的遊戲：麥當勞員工NDS培訓遊戲卡帶","createTime":"2021-04-12T21:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T19:15:02.000Z","uid":58576,"like":121,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"26f1b5f1fcef59f03e09270134b52ff099ba7ab3","tid":2486304,"uid":58576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T21:37:37.000Z","msg":"遊戲機除了拿來玩遊戲還能幹嘛呢？<br />\n<br />\n在智慧型手機尚未推出的年代，任天堂推出的掌機「NDS」可以說是當時世界上銷售量最高的攜帶裝置，而隨著羅浮宮導覽等等的NDS軟體推出後，任天堂更有進一步將這台遊戲機推廣到世界各地當作「各種APP」的載體裝置。<br />\n而在2010年時，麥當勞突然宣布與任天堂達成戰略合作，將花費220萬日幣開發麥當勞企業軟體，並且再額外採購消息，有很長一段時間，世界無數的任天堂收藏家都在找這片傳說中的「麥當勞NDS遊戲片」，為了就是將這段所剩不多的任天堂企業史收藏起來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYzH4ktsQAvv3aW1YxcJdL1cwKBb3DjYijsNBezsjY3hG?filename=0gHjbQe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0gHjbQe.jpg&h=21cc0c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但隨著這片遊戲的數量稀少，以及可靠消息來源短缺，更多的收藏家開始相信，所謂的麥當勞遊戲只不過是媒體為了炒作的所發的假新聞罷了，事實上根本沒有這片遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n然而2018年有了全新的消息，一名法國人宣稱他有這樣一片遊戲軟體，也給了遊戲截圖，但無奈破解不了一開始的密碼，也不願將遊戲軟體的內碼抽取出來交給專家，因此直接沒有了下文。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5431/5431838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5431%2F5431838.jpg&h=ad4e4662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n直到了2020年6月，日本雅虎拍賣出現了一個商品貼文，不只有完整的麥當勞遊戲片，甚至連當時採購的麥當勞NDS特仕機也一起販售，最後被一個美國的懷舊Youtuber以3400美金買下，然後運送的過程並不是十分順利，經過了許多磨難後，他終於拿到了夢幻的麥當勞特別版NDS，但礙於沒有密碼，他最終聯繫到了2018年那位法國人，那位法國人為了破解出密碼，找了很多當時日本麥當勞內部的原始文件，但仍然不能順利幫那位美國Youtuber破解密碼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeEScAnPNpBEtFPbRe4hdpyzcx3Ds5j1mrtB3abLLSn68?filename=mfUNkKg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfUNkKg.jpg&h=4f879a23&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n而就在近期這位美國Youtuber也意外自行破解了密碼，他發現密碼僅是簡單的00000，非常有可能是員工自行重設的，如今他也將遊戲的內容拍成影片，並把軟體從卡帶導出放到網上公開給大家下載，遊戲就是簡單的麥當勞基層員工生產餐點的基礎模擬軟體與教學，包括炸薯條、翻漢堡肉等等，如今這個長達10年以上的都市傳說真相終於得以出現在世人面前。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5431/5431840.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5431%2F5431840.jpg&h=1aca301e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5431/5431839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5431%2F5431839.jpg&h=61e446fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5431/5431841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5431%2F5431841.jpg&h=d6603080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"> 【The 10-Year Hunt for the Lost McDonald's DS Game】</span><br />\n<span class=\"small\">閞於這位 Youtuber Nick Robinson 得到遊戲卡帶和遊戲機過程的紀錄片</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-e6xOBCAVvA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-e6xOBCAVvA&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=2fa5a993\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-e6xOBCAVvA</a><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><span class=\"pink\">中國B站有中英字幕翻譯，但不分享連結</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"green\">後續發展</span></span><br />\n遊戲的Rom被公開後，麥當勞員工培訓遊戲成為Speed Runner(競速破關者)的新目標，其中炸薯條是最熱門的競速項目<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQVo7SL7dpaVHKMiTgR5V5yTko5MvDHhKvXN9L6g6qxGc?filename=GwrTgr6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwrTgr6.png&h=650a8446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除此之外， Nick Robinson發現eCDP外麥當勞還有三款DS遊戲存在<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPUzPgnoz5Tvqzy77As2mfMVNuAgT95b1HruG4ZW3dYke?filename=s6gG9Qa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs6gG9Qa.png&h=5786cda3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><em><span class=\"pink\">eSMART、eSMART 2.0</span></em></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR6QfUCSag1DxpHp7hYWmzxdhhwuiQcau1V1ZZ14ZDoju?filename=hDHnUjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDHnUjH.jpg&h=cfcb3da4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSWPyfPBGCEJHb6KeDwUoQGqNAFcMgA7ZmBYKQyhi3LST?filename=QXFEb6n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXFEb6n.jpg&h=892a020e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <span class=\"x-small\"><em><span class=\"pink\">還有DS Mac Adventure</span></em></span><br />\n資料來源 及 文章來源<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ecdp.tech/games/ecdp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ecdp.tech%2Fgames%2Fecdp.html&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=5f2a2525\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ecdp.tech/games/ecdp.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/babylonian/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fbabylonian%2Fvideos&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=460abc19\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/babylonian/videos</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/53337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F53337&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=d155ddfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/53337</a>"},{"pid":"cdab08f5406825038c97a826d7aeccbf90773be1","tid":2486304,"uid":6684,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T21:52:30.000Z","msg":"密碼=00000"},{"pid":"ea9fd7317a1363458357d1f83c8536f130e3fb53","tid":2486304,"uid":18691,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"cdab08f5406825038c97a826d7aeccbf90773be1","tid":2486304,"uid":6684,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T21:52:30.000Z","msg":"密碼=00000"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T21:53:51.000Z","msg":"password = password?"},{"pid":"41434adb1a95fe79a5ddf2355a219b11b49727d8","tid":2486304,"uid":117893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T22:12:12.000Z","msg":"想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmo